Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.83,0:00:02.57,OPC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)\be1}独自一人
Dialogue: 0,0:00:02.89,0:00:08.76,OPC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)\be1}迷失在旅途之中
