Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.24,0:00:25.53,OPC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)\be1}却阔步迈向远方
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.83,0:00:29.98,OPC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)\be1}于是与你在路上
