Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.11,0:00:56.96,OPC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)\be1}梦里见到的世界
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.20,0:01:01.13,OPC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)\be1}究竟在何处
